::Battera::

She heard him on her link.  She responded,"Yes, Please wait a few 
moments."  

She turned and looked at Iron Raptor. "That is my partner.  Please 
allow him entrance.  He is hear to help with the peace nagotiations. 
He is the one who will take you to the embassy. "  She didn't know is 
she would allow CyberShark into the base.  She still kept her hopes 
up though.
